Editor's Note:  Council Members Baez, Mendez, and Weprin were not present at the Stated Council Meeting held on June 12, 2008 but were present at the continuation of this Meeting during the Recessed Meeting of June 12, 2008 held on June 23, 2008.  With this in mind, Council Members Baez, Mendez, and Weprin are now considered present for the official Stated Council Meeting of June 12, 2008.  In addition, Council Member Weprin chose to take the opportunity at the Recessed Meeting held on June 23, 2008 to vote for the Land Use Call-up items of June 12, 2008 and also voted for the items Coupled on the General Order Calendar of June 12, 2008.  Council Members Baez and Mendez, however, did not vote for the June 12 items and are considered Present but Not Voting.

The newly revised vote for the Land Use Call-ups is now 48-0-0 with 2 Council Members Present but Not Voting (CMs Baez and Mendez);
the newly revised General Order vote for June 12 is now 48-0-0 with 2 Council Members Present but Not Voting.  The revised individual item votes are shown below.
